{"tid":2183473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教會Google Meet辦中國政教講座　「中国国安局香港分局」等3不明帳號闖入踢走牧師　疑全程被監控","createTime":"2020-09-01T03:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T16:28:00.000Z","uid":34409,"like":214,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"7843bd4d15ded762c1eaf7f85a86168ff4420aaf","tid":2183473,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"中華基督教會屯門堂星期日（30日）透過通訊軟件Google Meet，舉行一個名為「紅旗下十架的歷史變遷」講座，內容主要圍繞中國的政教關係。講座甫開始，分別有自稱「中國國安局香港分局」、「中國國家安全局」、「Shenzhengovernment」（深圳政府）的用戶要求加入，講座管理員拒絕。在講座尾聲，屯門堂堂主任陳勉宜牧師向參加者報告事件，發言中途不斷被第三方移除出聊天室，講座最後被逼終止。陳牧懷疑有國安部門監聽講座，他強調該講座是介紹中國教會政策的歷史，並無觸及國安法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全文請入<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/33465/google_meet-%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7-33465/%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83google-meet%E8%BE%A6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E6%95%99%E8%AC%9B%E5%BA%A7-%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%88%86%E5%B1%80%E3%80%8D%E7%AD%893%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F%E9%97%96%E5%85%A5%E8%B8%A2%E8%B5%B0%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB-%E7%96%91%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E8%A2%AB%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F33465%2Fgoogle_meet-%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1-%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%258E%25A7-33465%2F%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259C%2583google-meet%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%25BA%25A7-%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25B1%2580%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%25AD%25893%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E8%2599%259F%25E9%2597%2596%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%258E%25A7&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7obCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=65ebe8d6\" target=\"_blan