拆除違法建築，尤其為打壓宗教，下令大拆十字架和教堂，幾年間全省至少強拆2,000多間教堂和十字架，引發爭議，有數百萬天主教和基督教信眾的浙江省天怒人怨，連梵蒂岡也看不過眼，譴責浙江當局做法。夏寶龍因此被民間形容為「十字架殺手」。"},{"pid":"5336493fa4327abc97953612e2ba25d32f58705e","tid":2183473,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bf772fa7786ea43ca24889eff13a658cb4fc32","tid":2183473,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"奶共呀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f49982fda8736161dca7667902adb007723b26c","tid":2183473,"uid":132302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb4d72665cf3b9011ee3d9317a4da65b35172350","tid":2183473,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaeedd8a5cab09ce6c8ea1f4dd7121b80732602a","tid":2183473,"uid":135867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"48d220d7776c046f1443767187808e804f97c450","tid":2183473,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"各位搞清楚件事先<br />\nGoogle meet係有link就入得<br />\n唔係好似zoom咁可以控制<br />\n尤其是google meet好多參與者只係用網頁版本"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"屯門堂堂主任陳勉宜牧師向參加者報告事件，發言中途不斷被第三方移除出聊天室<br />\n夠唔夠清楚"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:50:13.000Z","msg":"應該任何人都可以踢人出聊天室<br />\n<br />\n因為google meet每次設立一個會議有一條link<br />\n呢條link係可以永久長存(唔跟會議book嘅時間)<br />\n唔似zoom咁每次會議都會有link<br />\n只要有valid link, 唔需要有host就可以入<br />\n所以所有人嘅權限係一樣<br />\n唔只係發起者可以踢人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"咁撚on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b842af9153dd134fe536b1c1cf85755c43706ba","tid":2183473,"uid":106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb4